# Cloudflare Pages redirects — source-path aliases → canonical pages (301 permanent).
# NOTE: this is a Cloudflare Pages feature. It is INERT on the GitHub Pages testing host and
# takes effect only once the site is served from Cloudflare Pages. It deploys only because it is
# listed in _config.yml `include:` — Jekyll ignores underscore-prefixed files by default.

/about-us              /about    301
/contact-us            /contact  301
/tos                   /terms    301
/terms-and-conditions  /terms    301
/terms-conditions      /terms    301
/terms-of-service      /terms    301
